idinfo.accconst: Data will be made available free of charge for all internal purposes and for those companies with contracts in good standing with the City of Norfolk. Additionally data will be provided to the federal government upon request and to other localities for the purpose of mutual aid response. All others are required to purchase the data from the City of Norfolk, Department of Planning & Community Development. 757-664-4752
idinfo.useconst: Any and all data sets are for graphical representations only and should not be used for legal purposes. Any determination of topography or contours, or any depiction of physical improvements, property lines or boundaries is for general information only and shall not be used for the design, modification, or construction of improvement to real property or for flood plain determination.
